Watch Jerma985's live streams at https://www.twitch.tv/jerma985.

Archive videos are recorded and edited through means reliant on personal convenience and Twitch's web playback performance. Imperfections such as buffering, audiovisual artifacts, and de-synchronization may occur.

Disclaimer: My channel is not affiliated with Jerma985 or related parties. Content on this channel is for my personal use and may vary in all aspects, face removal, or cease entirely for any reason. Subscribing is not recommended.
